title: N Biren Singh To Be Manipur Chief Minister Again, BJP Ends Suspense - NDTV
content: N Biren Singh To Be Manipur Chief Minister Again, BJP Ends Suspense  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: N Biren Singh has been chosen as Manipur Chief Minister for a second time. Ten days after election results came, the BJP today announced Mr Singh as the Chief Minister among two more contenders - Biswajit Singh and Yumnam Khemchand.
